title: 093 - Which Fictional Quarterback Are You Starting A Franchise With?
description: On today’s show, the boys dive through a loaded Pod FOD that includes more testimonials of people pooping in the shower, anteaters resisting arrest, which fictional quarterback the guys would start a franchise with, which old snack they’d like to see back in stores, how Connor’s identity theft case is going, and each of the guys sends in a song for this week’s edition of Friday Bangerz to help send you into the best weekend of all-time. Keep sending your submissions to the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. We appreciate you all for listening, enjoy.
